sequenceDiagram
    actor Prospect
    participant Agent
    participant Stripe
    participant DB
    participant Mail

    Prospect->>Agent: reply yes
    Agent->>Mail: CHECKOUT email with link
    Mail->>Prospect: delivered
    Prospect->>Stripe: click checkout link
    Stripe-->>Prospect: hosted checkout page
    Prospect->>Stripe: enter card and pay
    Stripe->>Agent: checkout.session.completed
    Agent->>DB: create PodcastSubscription
    Agent->>DB: create Podcast with defaults
    Agent->>DB: create PodcastAccessToken
    Agent->>Mail: ACCESS READY with feed URL
    Mail->>Prospect: delivered
    Note over Prospect,Mail: 24 hours later
    Agent->>Mail: EPISODE 1 PREVIEW
